query: SELECT p.*, s.name, s.smshubCode, s.active as service_active, c.smshubId as country_smshubId FROM prices p JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa' AND c.smshubId IS NOT NULL AND c.smshubId != 999 AND s.smshubCode IS NOT NULL
